CHILD SAFETY & CONTENT POLICY

This software is designed for educational purposes for children aged 2-5 years.

DEVELOPER RESPONSIBILITIES:
- Keep all content age-appropriate
- No external links or ads
- No personal data collection
- No tracking or analytics
- No inappropriate content
- Regular security updates

PARENTAL NOTICE:
- Always supervise children during use
- Check game content regularly
- Report inappropriate content
- Review privacy settings
- Set time limits

For more information, contact: support@miniGamesPAUD.com
